# {{SECTION}}/{{PLATFORM}}/{{NAME}}

{{PURPOSE}}

RunPod module. Uses the RunPod GraphQL API via `null_resource` + `curl`. Same pattern as `ai/LLMs/runpod` and `ai/NIMs/runpod`.

## Usage

```hcl
module "{{NAME}}" {
  source = "git::https://github.com/<org>/terraform-demo-modules.git//{{SECTION}}/{{PLATFORM}}/{{NAME}}?ref=vX.Y.Z"

  enable_{{NAME}}  = true
  runpod_api_key  = var.runpod_api_key
}
```

## Cost warning

RunPod GPU pods are billed per second. Always `terraform destroy` after a demo, or use the dashboard to stop the pod.

